2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the implementation and attack on a convolutional neural network accelerator, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper deals with deep learning models and their privacy concerns, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
4. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the implementation of a deep learning model on an FPGA-based accelerator, which falls under the scope of software engineering. 
5. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper discusses the implementation of a convolutional neural network accelerator on an FPGA, which falls under the scope of hardware architecture.
